Accommodations

There are no hotels directly on campus, but we recommend nearby options for symposium attendees:

  • Fairfield Inn & Suites Kennett Square 719 East Baltimore Pike, Kennett Square, PA (approx. 20 minutes from campus)

Questions

If you have any questions regarding travel arrangements, hotel accommodations, or block rates, please contact wmorgan@lincoln.edu

We encourage all attendees to book early in order to secure the best available rates within the hotel block.
